casebody.data:
No. 08-9723. Terrance Moore, Petitioner v. Ohio. 559 U.S. 967, 130 S. Ct. 1685,

176 L. Ed. 2d 176,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2024. March 1, 2010.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Ohio, Cuyahoga. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Court of Appeals of Ohio, Cuyahoga County, for further consideration in light of Melendez-Diaz v. Massachusetts, 557 U.S. 305, 129 S. Ct. 2527, 174 L. Ed. 2d 314 (2009).
